ies requires the local resolution to be automatically adapted in order to capture all the necessary flow features. If a single resolution is used throughout the domain, the number of particles would be excessively large. Solution method: We validate and demonstrate the accuracy of the adaptive particle refinement algorithm in simulating flow past moving multiple geometries. Our algorithm is fully parallel, and we provide an open-source implementation.},
